        "title": "Make Augment keepalive stop idempotent",
        "body": "## Summary\nSkip Augment keepalive stop work when no keepalive is active, avoiding repeated stop logs for already-stopped runtimes.\n\n## Validation\n- `swift test --filter AugmentStatusProbeTests`\n- `make check`\n- `git diff --check`\n\n## Runtime Proof\nPushed focused regression coverage at `765744b5`.\n\nIdempotent disabled-stop proof:\n\n```text\n$ swift test --filter AugmentProviderRuntimeTests 2>&1 | tee /tmp/codexbar-pr1262-runtime-proof.log\nTest Case `-[CodexBarTests.AugmentProviderRuntimeTests test_disabledStopIsIdempotent]` passed\nExecuted 1 test, with 0 failures\n\n$ rg \"Augment keepalive stopped\" /tmp/codexbar-pr1262-runtime-proof.log\n# no matches\n```\n\nCompatibility check:\n\n```text\n$ swift test --filter AugmentStatusProbeTests\nExecuted 17 tests, with 0 failures\n```\n\nAlso ran `git diff --check`; it passed with no output. The proof transcript omits local paths and unrelated provider-mode log noise.",
